room_title: Escape room "BattleShip" by Escape Newport News in Newport News
room_address: 5007 Victory Blvd., Unit D-2, Yorktown, VA 23693
room_description: The only competition escape room on the Peninsula, Battleship is a state-of-the-art generation two escape room. Battleship is a competition room with two separate, identical rooms. Each Battleship room holds up to 10 people, making the full capacity of Battleship 20 people!
